title: For Sale:  JC Higgins Model 51 RARE 30-06 Belgium FN Mauser NICE
postcontent: I am looking to sell my 1950 something JC Higgins Model 51 30-06. My gun is in as nice of condition as you could hope to find one of these in. Extremely nice. No rust or blue loss and wood is 99%. These guns were made by High Standard for Higgins from1950-55 from what Ive read. They made a few but the model 51 is the rare one and this one is even more rare because they were offered in 3 different actions. This is the belgium FN Mauser large ring 98 action, they also later made a sako action and a Husquavarna action. The barrel is a chrome lined high standard barrel and is mint. The SureFire M900 Vertical Foregrip WeaponLight delivers the tactical advantages of increased weapon control plus 500 lumens of ultra-reliable LED illumination. The light output is focused by a TIR lens into an intense, comparatively tight beam capable of illuminating mid-range targets and beyond, along with providing significant surround light for peripheral vision. The M900 also features two low-output LED navigation lights.
